<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ID Verification Notification</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    h2 {
      color: white;
    }

    section {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 20px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      We regret to inform you that your ID verification has been rejected. This may be due to an incorrect NIN number or the image provided not meeting our requirements. To proceed, kindly log in to your account and submit a new verification request with the correct details.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can access your account by clicking <a href="{{link}}">here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
    </p>
    <p>
      Best regards,<br />
      The Thriftify Team
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
